SPELL Q
Storm Bolt
deal Heavy damage to a target stunning them and reducing magic resist and armor also pushing the target back

damage 5 20 35 50 plus 40% of strenght -damage type MAGICAL-
cast range 700
push force 600
magic resist lost 7% 9% 11% 13%
armor lost 1 2 3 4
stun duration 2 3 4 5 last half on bosses
cooldown 8 10 12 14
mana cost 75 plus 2% 3% 4% 5% of max mana

talent level 10 upgrade Storm Bolt
increase damage by 20
increase strenght scaling by 12%
increase cast range by 300
increase push force by 100
increase the magic resist lost by 5%
stun duration last full on bosses as well

add a new modifier Violent Bolt
after hiting the target it will send other storm bolt to near enemy in a radius of 350
of the explosion of the first one and dealing full damage to the other target as well
if there is no one around storm bolt damage change to pure and deal 3% of the target max life
as damage


SPELL W
Thunder Clap
Muradin Smash the ground, dealing damage and slowing attack speed and movement speed. The more enemy hit
by this spell the more damage it deal

damage 11 14 17 20 plus 10% of strenght -damage type PURE-
radius 320 340 360 380
attack spell lost 15 20 25 30
movement speed lost 10% 16% 22% 28%
bonus damage per enemy 1 2 3 4
debuff duration 3 4 5 6
cooldown 9
mana cost 70 110 140 170 plus 1% of max mana

talent level 10 Upgrade Thunder Clap
increase damage by 10
increase strenght scaling by 10%
increase radius by 60
increase bonus damage per enemy at all level to 5 -NOTE- the way i mean that, it get 5 damage for level 1 2 3 and 4

add a new mofidier Hammer of Thunder
went Muradin do Thunder Clap for every enemy hit he will get 3 bonus damage for 5 second
and Thunder Clap deal 2% of the current life of the enemy as bonus damage he also heal for 1% of is
max life per enemy hit


SPELL E
Thunder Punch
Muradin Punch out any enemy dealing Massive damage and knocking them back and any unit that get in the way
of that enemy knock away will get stun and get damage as well

damage 20 40 60 80 plus 60% of strenght -damage type PURE-
enemy max health as damage 1% 2% 3% 4%
knock distence 600 800 1000 1200 boss will be knock for 500 distence
stun duration 1 second
cooldown 40 39 38 37
mana cost 125 150 175 200 plus 6% of max mana

talent level 15 upgrade Thunder Punch
increase damage by 10
increase strenght scaling by 20%
increase enemy max health as damage by 2%
increase stun duration by 0.5 second

add a new modifier Lightning Explosion
went Muradin punch the target, that target will release a lightning Bolt for every enemy that get hit by
Thunder Punch dealing 35 damage pure those enemy lose 35% damage and making that unit blind for 7 second
getting 20% chance to miss


